  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The primary endpoint is Investigator's Clinical efficacy at Day 8.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Endpoints of efficacy are as follows: Investigator's clinical efficacy (at Day 4, Day 15 and 29) Bacteriological efficacy (at Day 4, 8, 15 and 29) Safety Endpoints: Adverse events and safety Laboratory data</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
